items.title: How big U.S. bank BNY manages armies of AI agents
items.description: As investment bank BNY plans to upgrade its AI tool Eliza, it's looking forward to creating smart recommendation AI agents.

items.title: Google makes Gemini Code Assist free with 180,000 code completions per month as AI-powered dev race heats up
items.description: Google’s decision to provide a free version with significantly higher usage limits positions Gemini Code Assist as a compelling choice.

items.title: Adobe launches first Photoshop mobile app and it has amazing Firefly AI-powered object detection, editing, and effects
items.description: Photoshop mobile includes Firefly-powered gen AI features like Generative Fill and Generative Expand and has mobile-adjusted touch targets.

items.title: Prompt AI’s Seemour launches visual intelligence platform for the home
items.description: Prompt AI, a smart home and visual intelligence research and technology company, has launched Seemour, a visual intelligence platform.

items.title: Quantum Machines raises $170M to accelerate adoption of quantum computing
items.description: Quantum Machines has raised $170 million in funding to accelerate quantum computing and improve its advanced quantum control solutions.
